    <title>hexo博客搭建</title>
    <link href="/2026/01/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <url>/2026/01/10/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>这篇就是给未来的自己看的：如果哪天把博客环境搞乱了，照着这篇一步一步重来就行</p></blockquote><h2 id="博客写作"><a href="#博客写作" class="headerlink" title="博客写作"></a>博客写作</h2><ul><li>目前日常写博客就用obsidian，切换到blog工作区写就好了</li><li>平板与电脑都有一个此工作区，写完同步就好了</li><li>电脑做git提交，bat脚本运行就好了</li></ul><h2 id="一、整体目标"><a href="#一、整体目标" class="headerlink" title="一、整体目标"></a>一、整体目标</h2><ol><li>本地用 Hexo + Fluid 写博客、预览效果；</li><li>源码放在一个 Git 仓库（以下简称“源码仓库”）；</li><li>生成好的静态文件通过 GitHub Actions 自动推送到 <code>roiiou/roiiou.github.io</code>（以下简称“Pages 仓库”）；</li><li>最终访问地址是：<code>https://roiiou.github.io</code>。</li></ol><p>整个流程：</p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs text">本地写作 → git push 源码仓库 main → GitHub Actions 构建 Hexo → 部署到 roiiou.github.io(master) → 访问 https://roiiou.github.io<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="二、本地环境与项目初始化（一次性工作）"><a href="#二、本地环境与项目初始化（一次性工作）" class="headerlink" title="二、本地环境与项目初始化（一次性工作）"></a>二、本地环境与项目初始化（一次性工作）</h2><h3 id="1-安装-Node-js-和-Hexo-CLI"><a href="#1-安装-Node-js-和-Hexo-CLI" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装 Node.js 和 Hexo CLI"></a>1. 安装 Node.js 和 Hexo CLI</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-初始化-Hexo-项目"><a href="#2-初始化-Hexo-项目" class="headerlink" title="2. 初始化 Hexo 项目"></a>2. 初始化 Hexo 项目</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo init blog<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> blog<br>npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>之后本地项目根目录就是：<code>D:\blog</code>。</p><hr><h2 id="三、通过-npm-安装-Fluid-主题"><a href="#三、通过-npm-安装-Fluid-主题" class="headerlink" title="三、通过 npm 安装 Fluid 主题"></a>三、通过 npm 安装 Fluid 主题</h2><h3 id="1-安装主题和渲染器"><a href="#1-安装主题和渲染器" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装主题和渲染器"></a>1. 安装主题和渲染器</h3><p>在 <code>D:\blog</code> 下执行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-theme-fluid --save<br>npm install hexo-renderer-ejs hexo-renderer-stylus --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-在-config-yml-中启用-Fluid（npm-版）"><a href="#2-在-config-yml-中启用-Fluid（npm-版）" class="headerlink" title="2. 在 _config.yml 中启用 Fluid（npm 版）"></a>2. 在 <code>_config.yml</code> 中启用 Fluid（npm 版）</h3><p><code>_config.yml</code> 中关键配置现在是：</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://roiiou.github.io</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">root:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Extensions</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">fluid</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">theme_dir:</span> <span class="hljs-string">node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：</p><ul><li><code>url</code> 必须是 <code>https://&lt;用户名&gt;.github.io</code>，不要写 GitHub 仓库地址；</li><li>主页仓库的 <code>root</code> 就是 <code>/</code>；</li><li><code>theme_dir</code> 指向 npm 安装的 <code>node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid</code>，不会再依赖 <code>themes/fluid</code> 目录。</li></ul><h3 id="3-配置-config-fluid-yml"><a href="#3-配置-config-fluid-yml" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置 _config.fluid.yml"></a>3. 配置 <code>_config.fluid.yml</code></h3><p><code>_config.fluid.yml</code> 用来定制 Fluid 的外观，例如站点名、横幅、主题色等等（这里只记要点）：</p><ul><li><code>site.name</code>：导航栏左上角的名字；</li><li><code>banner.img</code>：首页大图（目前我用的是一张放在 COS 上的图片）；</li><li><code>theme_color.main</code>：主题主色；</li><li>其它如：评论、统计、搜索等后面再慢慢开。</li></ul><p>改完以后本地验证：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npx hexo clean<br>npx hexo g<br>npx hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览器打开 <code>http://localhost:4000</code>，确认已经是 Fluid 主题、横幅和样式都正常。</p><hr><h2 id="四、GitHub-Pages-双仓库结构"><a href="#四、GitHub-Pages-双仓库结构" class="headerlink" title="四、GitHub Pages 双仓库结构"></a>四、GitHub Pages 双仓库结构</h2><p>这里采用的是 <strong>Hexo 官方推荐的双仓库方案</strong>：</p><ul><li>源码仓库：存 Hexo 源码（<code>source/</code>、<code>_config*.yml</code>、<code>package.json</code> 等）；</li><li>Pages 仓库：<code>roiiou/roiiou.github.io</code>，只存 <code>public/</code> 里的静态文件，由 GitHub Pages 直接发布。</li></ul><p>Pages 仓库设置：</p><ul><li>打开 <code>roiiou/roiiou.github.io</code> → <code>Settings</code> → <code>Pages</code>；</li><li>Source 设置为：<code>Deploy from a branch</code>；</li><li>Branch 选择：<code>master</code>，目录 <code>/ (root)</code>。</li></ul><hr><h2 id="五、GitHub-Actions-自动构建与部署"><a href="#五、GitHub-Actions-自动构建与部署" class="headerlink" title="五、GitHub Actions 自动构建与部署"></a>五、GitHub Actions 自动构建与部署</h2><h3 id="1-新建工作流文件"><a href="#1-新建工作流文件" class="headerlink" title="1. 新建工作流文件"></a>1. 新建工作流文件</h3><p>在源码仓库中新建：<code>.github/workflows/deploy.yml</code>，核心内容如下（当前正在使用的版本）：</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Hexo</span> <span class="hljs-string">Auto</span> <span class="hljs-string">Deploy</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">on:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">push:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">branches:</span> [ <span class="hljs-string">main</span> ]<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">paths:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;source/**&quot;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;themes/**&quot;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;_config.yml&quot;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;_fluid_config.yml&quot;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;package.json&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">jobs:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">build-deploy:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="hljs-string">ubuntu-latest</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">steps:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">📥</span> <span class="hljs-string">拉取源码（含themes/fluid）</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">uses:</span> <span class="hljs-string">actions/checkout@v4</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">with:</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">ref:</span> <span class="hljs-string">main</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">fetch-depth:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">🟢</span> <span class="hljs-string">配置Node.js环境</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">uses:</span> <span class="hljs-string">actions/setup-node@v4</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">with:</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">node-version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;20.x&quot;</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">cache:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;npm&quot;</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">🔧</span> <span class="hljs-string">安装Hexo及项目依赖（含npm版</span> <span class="hljs-string">Fluid</span> <span class="hljs-string">主题）</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">|</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          npm install</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          npm install hexo-theme-fluid --save</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          npm install hexo-renderer-ejs hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="hljs-string"></span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">🧹</span> <span class="hljs-string">强制清理Hexo缓存和旧静态文件</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">|</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          hexo clean --force</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          rm -rf ./public</span><br><span class="hljs-string"></span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">🏗️</span> <span class="hljs-string">生成静态网页（使用npm+配置的Fluid主题）</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">|</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          hexo generate</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          echo &quot;===== 生成的主题CSS文件 =====&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          ls -la public/css/</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          echo &quot;===== 生成的主题JS文件 =====&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          ls -la public/js/</span><br><span class="hljs-string"></span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">🚀</span> <span class="hljs-string">部署到GitHub</span> <span class="hljs-string">Pages</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">env:</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">PAT:</span> <span class="hljs-string">$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="hljs-string">secrets.HEXO_DEPLOY_PAT</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#125;&#125;</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">GIT_USER:</span> <span class="hljs-string">roiiou</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">GIT_EMAIL:</span> <span class="hljs-string">rou819@qq.com</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">TARGET_REPO:</span> <span class="hljs-string">roiiou/roiiou.github.io</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">|</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          git config --global user.name &quot;$GIT_USER&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          git config --global user.email &quot;$GIT_EMAIL&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          cd public</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          git init</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          git add .</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          git commit -m &quot;Deploy $(date +&#x27;%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S&#x27;)&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          DEPLOY_URL=&quot;https://$&#123;PAT&#125;@github.com/$&#123;TARGET_REPO&#125;.git&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          git push --force &quot;$DEPLOY_URL&quot; master:master</span><br><span class="hljs-string">          echo &quot;✅ 部署完成！访问：https://roiiou.github.io&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>要点：</p><ol><li>Action 使用 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 <code>theme: fluid</code> + <code>theme_dir</code>，不再在脚本里 <code>hexo config theme ...</code>；</li><li>通过 npm 安装 <code>hexo-theme-fluid</code>，保证云端和本地主题版本一致；</li><li>生成后进入 <code>public/</code>，重新 <code>git init</code>，<strong>强制推送到 Pages 仓库的 <code>master</code> 分支</strong>；</li><li>Pages 仓库的 GitHub Pages 设置为：<code>master</code> 分支根目录。</li></ol><h3 id="2-Personal-Access-Token（PAT）"><a href="#2-Personal-Access-Token（PAT）" class="headerlink" title="2. Personal Access Token（PAT）"></a>2. Personal Access Token（PAT）</h3><p>为了让 Actions 能往 <code>roiiou.github.io</code> 推代码，需要一个 PAT：</p><ol><li>GitHub 右上角头像 → <code>Settings</code> → <code>Developer settings</code> → <code>Personal access tokens</code>；</li><li>生成一个 token（选 classic 或 fine-grained 都行，最少需要对 <code>roiiou.github.io</code> 有 <code>contents: write</code> 权限）；</li><li>复制 Token 值；</li><li>在 <strong>源码仓库</strong> 的 <code>Settings</code> → <code>Secrets and variables</code> → <code>Actions</code> 中添加：<ul><li>Name：<code>HEXO_DEPLOY_PAT</code></li><li>Value：刚才复制的 token</li></ul></li></ol><p>Action 中就是通过 <code>$&#123;&#123; secrets.HEXO_DEPLOY_PAT &#125;&#125;</code> 来使用这个 token。</p><hr>]]></content>
    
    
